items.title: Intuit tops Wall Street estimates after tax season, issues strong guidance
items.description: Intuit reported better-than-expected results for the fiscal third quarter and also beat estimates with its full-year forecast.

items.title: Snowflake shares soar to highest level in over a year as revenue tops $1 billion for first time
items.description: Snowflake shares popped on Thursday after the data analytics company reported better-than-expected earnings and revenue.

items.title: Xpeng shares rise, adding to 66% rally after the Chinese EV maker's losses narrowed
items.description: Xpeng said it expects to deliver between 102,000 and 108,000 of its electric cars in the second quarter of this year.

items.title: Canada Goose shares soar nearly 20% as company beats estimates, pulls full-year guidance
items.description: Shares of Canada Goose rose 20% after the company reported fiscal fourth-quarter earnings that beat analysts' estimates.

items.title: Target cuts sales outlook as retailer blames tariff uncertainty and backlash to DEI rollback
items.description: Target missed first-quarter sales estimates and said it was setting up a new office to try to accelerate its turnaround.
